X-Temp technology is designed to adapt to your temperature and activity to keep you cool and dry for all day comfort. FreshIQ advanc edodor protection technology attacks the odor-causing bacteria in your clothing that causes your t-shirts to smell – so now you can feel fresh all day. Three-button placket with dyed-to-match buttons. All the comfort of Hanes with our famous tag-fre e neckline. Machine wash cold with like colors non chlorine bleach when needed tumble dry medium.

I wear it for running weight training yoga and just everyday activities. - Customer Reviews the Strategic Comfort Zones! Smooth lining and bottom band feel great against skin. Adjustable tag-free back has cushioned hook-and-eye closure.

post_content: Naturally breathable and soft against your skin, these cotton briefs are ideal for everyday wear. 100% preshrunk cotton. Cool Comfort® finish wicks moisture to keep you cool and dry. Convenient 6-pack in all white. Prefer a roomier fit? Go up one size. (Be sure to order based on the size chart.)

post_title: Champion Womens The Show-Off Sports Bra
post_content: True to promises! This is the only bra I use for HIIT and Zumba. It's thin conceals well is supportive and gives good shape - Customer ReviewFlaunt Your ShapeThe Show-Off Sports Bra checks all your boxes. No show-through. No bounce. No sweat!S moothmolded cups with concealing petals prevent show-through and provide Maximum Support. Moisture-wicking Champion Vapor technology lifts sweat away from skin for cooler drier comfort. Performance mesh (front and back) adds cooling ventilation. S oft cushioned inner seam gently contours your curves. Wide smooth bottom band adds extra support and comfort. Silky straps adjust in front for convenience. Tag-free T-back has cooling keyhole plus adjustable hook-and-eye closure for easy on/off.
